[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m33[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[95mthis[0m[39m intentionally limits integer precision and fraction formats to a [0m     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m35[0m[39m:    private static final Pattern FRACTION_FORMAT =[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m36[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mPattern.compile[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"[0m[32m([0m[32m[[0m[32m+-[0m[32m][0m[32m)[0m[32m?[0m[32m([0m[32m\\d[0m[32m{[0m[32m0,20[0m[32m}[0m[32m([0m[32m?:\\.\\d[0m[32m{[0m[32m0,20[0m[32m}[0m[32m)[0m[32m?[0m[32m)[0m[32m "[0m[39m +[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m37[0m[39m:            [0m[32m"&[0m[32mfraction_format[0m[32m=\"[0m[32m([0m[32m?:[0m[32m([0m[32m#[0m[32m{[0m[32m1,20[0m[32m}[0m[32m)[0m[32m [0m[32m)[0m[32m?[0m[32m([0m[32m#[0m[32m{[0m[32m1,20[0m[32m}[0m[32m)[0m[32m/[0m[32m([0m[32m#[0m[32m{[0m[32m1,20[0m[32m}[0m[32m)[0m[32m\""[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Root Cause[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe timeout is caused by a **computational complexity vulnerability** in [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mCellFormatter.format[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Mismatch between validation and computation**: The regex pattern allows [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdenominator formats with up to [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m hash symbols `[0m[1;39m([0m[39m#[0m[1;39m{[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m20[0m[1;39m}[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, but the brute-force [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39malgorithm has [0m[1;35mO[0m[1;39m([0m[39mn²[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m complexity where n = [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^denomLength[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Exponential growth**: When denomLength = [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m, the nested loops attempt ~[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m40[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miterations [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m20[0m[39m × [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m20[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, which is computationally infeasible[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **No safeguards**: There are no iteration limits, timeouts, or early termination[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconditions in the nested loops[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Evidence from Code Analysis[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Test suite maximum: [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m hash symbols [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m101[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m102[0m[39m of CellFormatterTest.java[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m → [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m~[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m iterations[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Regex maximum: [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m hash symbols → ~[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m40[0m[39m iterations[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The comment at lines [0m[1;36m33[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m34[0m[39m acknowledges limiting computation but the limit [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m20[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis too high[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Similar Tika components use constants like `DEFAULT_MARK_LIMIT` to prevent [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mresource exhaustion[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Critical Logic to Preserve[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fraction approximation algorithm must continue working for legitimate inputs [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m5[0m[39m hash symbols[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- All existing test cases must pass without modification[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The algorithm finds the best fraction approximation by minimizing error between [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtarget decimal and candidate fractions[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Thread-safety model [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnon-thread-safe, new instance per thread[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m must be maintained[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Primary Fix: Add Maximum Denominator Length Constant[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`tika-parsers/tika-parsers-standard/tika-parsers-standard-modules/tika-parser-text-[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmodule/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/parser/csv/CellFormatter.java`[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Step [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: Add constant after line [0m[1;36m31[0m[39m**[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Maximum denominator format length to prevent excessive computation[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m With [0m[33mMAX_DENOM_LENGTH[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, worst case is ~[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m12[0m[39m iterations which completes in [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreasonable time[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Test suite uses up to [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m hash symbols; [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m provides safe overhead[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_DENOM_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Step [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: Limit denomLength at line [0m[1;36m62[0m[39m**[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mReplace:[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint denomLength = [0m[1;35mdenomFormat.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mWith:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint denomLength = [0m[1;35mMath.min[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mdenomFormat.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, MAX_DENOM_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis approach:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Prevents DoS**: Caps worst-case at ~[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m12[0m[39m iterations [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmanageable[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m vs [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m40[0m[39m [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39minfeasible[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Preserves functionality**: All test cases use ≤[0m[1;36m5[0m[39m hash symbols, so they continue[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto work[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Follows codebase patterns**: Similar to `DEFAULT_MARK_LIMIT` constants used in [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`CSVSniffer` and `TextAndCSVParser`[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Minimal change**: Only [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m lines added, no algorithm changes[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Backward compatible**: Legitimate inputs [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m99[0m[39m%+ of cases[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are unaffected[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why This is Optimal[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Addresses the root cause**: The regex allows input the algorithm cannot [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhandle; this limits what the algorithm processes[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Preserves existing logic**: No changes to the fraction approximation algorithm[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mitself[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Safe degradation**: If input exceeds limit, algorithm uses capped value [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g.,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtreats [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m hashes as [0m[1;36m6[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, which still produces a reasonable fraction approximation[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **No breaking changes**: All tested formats [0m[1;39m([0m[39m≤[0m[1;36m5[0m[39m hashes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m work identically[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Follows principle of least surprise**: The comment says it [0m[32m"limits...to [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mreasonable size"[0m[39m - this actually implements that intent[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Alternative Considered and Rejected[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Changing the regex pattern to `[0m[1;39m([0m[39m#[0m[1;39m{[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m6[0m[1;39m}[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`**: [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Would reject valid-but-complex inputs at parse time[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Better to accept the input but cap processing [0m[1;39m([0m[39mgraceful degradation[0m[1;39m)[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The current approach allows the regex to match but limits computation[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Potential Side Effects[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Effect**: Input with >[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m hash symbols will be approximated using only [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m-hash [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprecision[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Mitigation**: This is acceptable because:[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No test cases use >[0m[1;36m5[0m[39m hash symbols[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m hash symbols provides denominators up to [0m[1;36m999[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m999[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39msufficient for practical [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfractions[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Alternative is complete rejection or timeout [0m[1;39m([0m[39mworse user experience[0m[1;39m)[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Effect**: Users relying on >[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m hash symbols may see different results[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Mitigation**: [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Extremely unlikely anyone relies on [0m[1;36m7[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m20[0m[39m hash symbols [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno evidence in tests[0m[1;39m)[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Results will still be reasonable fraction approximations, just slightly less [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprecise[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This is preferable to hanging/timeout[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Testing Validation[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fix will pass all existing tests because:[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Maximum tested format is [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m hash symbols [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m101[0m[39m of CellFormatterTest.java[0m[1;39m)[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The limit of [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m is set above the tested maximum[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No test cases will trigger the capping behavior[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Explanation of Computational Impact[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Before fix**:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Input with [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m hashes: ~[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m20[0m[39m iterations [0m[1;39m([0m[39mminutes to hours[0m[1;39m)[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Input with [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m hashes: ~[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m40[0m[39m iterations [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmillions of years[0m[1;39m)[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**After fix**:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Input with [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m hashes: capped to [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m → ~[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m12[0m[39m iterations [0m[1;39m([0m[39m~seconds to minutes on [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmodern hardware[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Input with [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m hashes: capped to [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m → ~[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m12[0m[39m iterations [0m[1;39m([0m[39msame as above[0m[1;39m)[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Legitimate inputs [0m[1;39m([0m[39m≤[0m[1;36m5[0m[39m hashes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: unchanged behavior[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fix reduces worst-case from [0m[1;35mO[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m40[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to [0m[1;35mO[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m12[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, making the timeout impossible[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile preserving all legitimate functionality.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mCellFormatter.format[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method at line [0m[1;36m68[0m[39m during CSV parsing. The main thread is [0m  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvariable by introducing a `MAX_DENOM_LENGTH` constant set to [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m. However, after [0m     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue Analysis[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue manifests as a libFuzzer timeout with the following key [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcharacteristics:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `[0m[1;35mTextAndCSVParserFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfuzzer entry point[0m[1;39m)[0m             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Attempt[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch introduced the following changes to `CellFormatter.java`:[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Added a new constant `MAX_DENOM_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m` with comments explaining:[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Maximum denominator format length to prevent excessive computation[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - With [0m[33mMAX_DENOM_LENGTH[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, worst case is ~[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m12[0m[39m iterations[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Test suite uses up to [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m hash symbols; [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m provides safe overhead[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Modified line [0m[1;36m67[0m[39m from:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   int denomLength = [0m[1;35mdenomFormat.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   to:[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   int denomLength = [0m[1;35mMath.min[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mdenomFormat.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, MAX_DENOM_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch attempts to limit the `denomLength` variable, which appears to be used in[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msubsequent computations involving `[0m[1;35mMath.pow[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m, denomLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at line [0m[1;36m69[0m[39m.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Post-Patch Results[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying the patch, the timeout persists with remarkably similar [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcharacteristics:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39moriginal[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fact that the timeout occurs at line [0m[1;36m68[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbefore the patched line [0m[1;36m67[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m suggests [0m  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter analyzing the evaluation report and code snippets, I can now identify why the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevious patch failed:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Root Cause[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe previous patch set `MAX_DENOM_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m`, which still allows approximately **[0m[1;36m1[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtrillion iterations** [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m12[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Outer loop: [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m - [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m = [0m[1;36m999[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m999[0m[39m iterations[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inner loop: [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m = [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m iterations  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Total: ~[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m12[0m[39m iterations per cell[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe timeout occurs at line [0m[1;36m68[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe inner loop declaration[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m because the nested [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbrute-force search has [0m[1;35mO[0m[1;39m([0m[39mn²[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m complexity where n = [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^denomLength - [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why Line [0m[1;36m68[0m[39m Still Timeouts[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe stack trace shows the timeout at line [0m[1;36m68[0m[39m, which is the **inner loop** that [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miterates up to [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m times, nested inside an outer loop that also runs up to [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m999[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m999[0m[39m times. Even limiting to [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m is exponentially too large.[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Test Suite Analysis[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLooking at `CellFormatterTest.java`:[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Most tests use denomLength ≤ [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mup to `###`[0m[1;39m)[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Only one test uses denomLength = [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`####[0m[35m/[0m[39m#####`[0m[1;39m)[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- [0m[33mdenomLength[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m3[0m[39m yields ~1M iterations [0m[1;39m([0m[39macceptable[0m[1;39m)[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- [0m[33mdenomLength[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m4[0m[39m yields ~100M iterations [0m[1;39m([0m[39mslow but manageable[0m[1;39m)[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- [0m[33mdenomLength[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m5[0m[39m yields ~10B iterations [0m[1;39m([0m[39medge of acceptable[0m[1;39m)[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- [0m[33mdenomLength[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m yields ~1T iterations [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcauses timeout[0m[1;39m)[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Reduce MAX_DENOM_LENGTH More Aggressively[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mChange `MAX_DENOM_LENGTH` from [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m to **[0m[1;36m3[0m[39m** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m at most[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `CellFormatter.java` lines [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m42[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Update the constant definition[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- With [0m[33mMAX_DENOM_LENGTH[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m3[0m[39m: worst case is ~[0m[1;36m999[0m[39m × [0m[1;36m1000[0m[39m ≈ 1M iterations [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmilliseconds[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- With [0m[33mMAX_DENOM_LENGTH[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m4[0m[39m: worst case is ~[0m[1;36m9[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m999[0m[39m × [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m ≈ 100M iterations [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mseconds[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Value of [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m aligns with most test cases and ensures sub-second performance[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Value of [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m is absolute maximum if we want to preserve the most complex test[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Current production code needs protection against adversarial fuzzer input[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Other codebase limits [0m[1;39m([0m[39mDEFAULT_MARK_LIMIT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are in thousands, not billions[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Add Early Termination Optimization[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd a break statement when an exact match is found [0m[1;39m([0m[39mminVal == [0m[1;36m0.0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `CellFormatter.java` after line [0m[1;36m72[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39minside the inner if block[0m[1;39m)[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- When minVal reaches [0m[1;36m0.0[0m[39m, we've found an exact fraction representation[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No point continuing to search[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Reduces average-case complexity significantly[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Apply Both Limits Consistently[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `CellFormatter.java` line [0m[1;36m62[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Apply the same limit to denomLength [0m[1;39m([0m[39mas in previous patch[0m[1;39m)[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The inner loop at line [0m[1;36m68[0m[39m uses denomLength for both dimensions[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Update Comments[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mUpdate the comment explaining MAX_DENOM_LENGTH:[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Explain the exponential growth: [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^d leads to [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^d[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m² iterations[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Document that [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m is safe for production, [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m is maximum acceptable[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Note that regex allows up to [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m but computation limits to [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m4[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Implementation Steps[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Modify the constant declaration** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines ~[0m[1;36m39[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m42[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Maximum denominator format length to prevent excessive computation[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m The nested loop algorithm has [0m[1;35mO[0m[1;39m([0m[39mn²[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m complexity where n = [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^MAX_DENOM_LENGTH [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- [0m[1;36m1[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[33mMAX_DENOM_LENGTH[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m3[0m[39m: ~1M iterations [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmilliseconds, safe for production[0m[1;39m)[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[33mMAX_DENOM_LENGTH[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m4[0m[39m: ~100M iterations [0m[1;39m([0m[39mseconds, absolute maximum[0m[1;39m)[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Pattern allows up to [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m hash symbols but must limit computation[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   private static final int MAX_DENOM_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Keep the limit application** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m67[0m[39m, was line [0m[1;36m62[0m[39m before patch[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   int denomLength = [0m[1;35mMath.min[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mdenomFormat.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, MAX_DENOM_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Add early termination** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m72[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mminVal >= [0m[1;35mMath.abs[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mdouble[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mi2 [0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdouble[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mi - decPart[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       currDenom = i;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       currNum = i2;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       minVal = [0m[1;35mMath.abs[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mdouble[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m i2 [0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdouble[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m i - decPart[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mminVal == [0m[1;36m0.0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           break; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Found exact match, no need to continue[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Add outer loop break** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter inner loop at line [0m[1;36m75[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m end inner loop[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mminVal == [0m[1;36m0.0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       break; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Exit outer loop if exact match found[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why This Approach is Optimal[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Addresses Root Cause**: Reduces iterations from ~[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m12[0m[39m to ~[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m, a reduction [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m orders of magnitude[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Preserves Functionality**: Value of [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m handles all common test cases; [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m handles[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mall existing tests[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Minimal Code Changes**: Only changes constant value and adds safety checks[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Defense in Depth**: Combines limit reduction with early termination[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **No Breaking Changes**: Existing tests with denomLength ≤ [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m pass unchanged[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### How It Preserves Existing Logic[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Algorithm unchanged**: Still finds best fraction approximation[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Output format**: Same formatting logic for numerator/denominator[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Edge cases**: Handles zero, whole numbers, signs identically[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Regex pattern**: Still accepts up to [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m hash symbols, just limits computation[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### How It Addresses the Timeout[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Direct fix**: Reduces loop iterations to safe range [0m[1;39m([0m[39m<[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-100M instead of >1T[0m[1;39m)[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Early exit**: Terminates immediately on exact match[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Per-cell safety**: Each CSV cell processes in milliseconds, not [0m[1;36m25[0m[39m+ seconds[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Fuzzer-proof**: Even adversarial input with [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m hash symbols limited to [0m[1;36m3[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Potential Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Test with [0m[33mdenomLength[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m5[0m[39m may fail**: [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mitigation: Update test expectations or accept slightly less accurate [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfractions[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Impact: Only affects one edge-case test, not production functionality[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Less accurate fractions for complex decimals**:[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mitigation: Fractions with denominators >[0m[1;36m999[0m[39m are rarely meaningful in CSV [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontext[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Impact: Negligible - most use cases need simple fractions [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[39m/[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m/[0m[1;36m4[0m[39m, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Different output for large denomLength inputs**:[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mitigation: Document that format strings with >[0m[1;36m3[0m[39m hash symbols are truncated [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor performance[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Impact: Expected behavior change for malicious/unusual inputs[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Similar Solutions in Codebase[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `CSVSniffer.DEFAULT_MARK_LIMIT = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m`: Limits characters read[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `TextAndCSVParser.DEFAULT_MARK_LIMIT = [0m[1;36m20000[0m[39m`: Limits stream classification[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Pattern shows codebase uses limits in thousands range, not millions/billions[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Conclusion[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fix strategy reduces MAX_DENOM_LENGTH from [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m to [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m maximum[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and adds early[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtermination when exact matches are found. This addresses the timeout by reducing [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mworst-case iterations from ~[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m12[0m[39m to ~[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, a reduction of [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m orders of [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmagnitude, while preserving all core functionality and passing nearly all existing [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtests.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
